text: Alibrandi is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Enrico Cruciani Alibrandi (1839–1921), Italian politician *Gaetano Alibrandi (1914–2003), Italian titular archbishops *Girolamo Alibrandi (1470–1524), Italian painter == See also == *Looking for Alibrandi (film), is an Australian film *Looking for Alibrandi (novel), novel of Australian author Melina Marchetta
